236
00:14:49,601 --> 00:14:50,992
and risking freedom,

237
00:14:52,282 --> 00:14:54,227
I believe it's a gamble worth taking.

238
00:14:56,547 --> 00:14:57,890
And what has it yielded?

239
00:14:59,805 --> 00:15:01,273
It has revealed to me that everyone

240
00:15:01,298 --> 00:15:03,164
