274
00:16:51,659 --> 00:16:54,322
because I will never harm Dech.

275
00:16:54,456 --> 00:16:55,656
Mark my words!

276
00:16:58,112 --> 00:16:59,455
Go wherever you want!

277
00:16:59,799 --> 00:17:01,721
